{
  "stem": "10181.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Simply the years-- the amount of years-- so many years had to go by.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But really to speak to schools and things like that, I only started after--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's later.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I started after that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But to me you start-- in trickles, I heard over the years, I heard bits and pieces.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Also, you know, when you see what goes on in the world today, you say to yourself, well, maybe not exactly the same thing can happen again.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it-- but it can happen again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It can even happen to the Jews, you know, who knows.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, this-- this-- like a famous professor said, you know, this wasn't just evil people who did this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "These were ordinary people who did this, ordinary like-- like everybody else.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It wasn't any special people, you know, who became-- who did these evil things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and-- people are very easily-led, and-- under certain conditions, especially.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, if you get a lot of unemployed, or you get a strong leader, you know, a strong person who-- who easily convinces people-- if you look what happens in Yugoslavia, if you look what happens in-- in-- in other places in the world, in Africa especially-- it's-- it's very-- what's the matter?",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's very easy to-- that things can happen again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and-- so, you know, I really feel that it's very important for the children to learn what happened to us, because the Holocaust was a unique experience.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was an attempt to wipe out a race, the Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, other-- other so-called holocausts were really for land.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "People wanted to-- to push the-- the Armenians out of certain areas when the Armenians in Armenia at one time were persecuted.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But Armenians living in-- in Istanbul were not touched because they were no threat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, they were not-- but the Jews were-- were-- were to be exterminated wherever they were.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, they were the enemy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You're becoming a big historian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and so it's really something which the kids-- if-- if the children don't learn about it, then it'll be lost in history.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I always say, when-- once we forget our past, it can happen again in the future.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, this is-- this is my message, you know, that we should remember where we came from, should remember our past, what happened to us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As long as we remember, we have to forgive but we cannot forget.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Once we forget, then we have the danger of it happening again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this is why it's so important to teach the young, because they are the ones who-- the-- the next generation are the ones who are going to continue and-- and talk about it-- what they heard from their parents to the generations after.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is the Iron Cross.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father got the-- this decoration in the First World War.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is one of many, what he got.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This particular one was given to him in 1914.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] OK.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is my birth certificate, which was issued in 1938.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All the birth certificates up to then were-- were taken away, and these were re-issued.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if you notice, it says on it 'Fritz Israel Spiegel.' My name is not Israel, but every Jewish male had to be Israel, and every female, Sarah.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is-- this is a copy-- this is one of these-- not a copy-- this is original of a Red Cross letter, which we sent to my mother.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She sent to us, and we replied on it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You could send a letter through the Red Cross every month and write 25 words.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So you said, we're feeling fine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Everything is good, and-- and-- hope to hear from you again soon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This is a DP card which was filled out in Maastricht by the authorities, affirm that we were repatriated.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- and this particular card-- as we were not Dutch citizens, we were given a DP card because we were foreigners, and they considered us displaced persons.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This is a picture of the local soccer team in Dinslaken.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Of my father was part of the soccer team.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This is in 1913, '14, before the war, just before the war--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First World War.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He is the third from the right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is my father and my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it's a photo taken, oh, at their wedding or at the honeymoon.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is my sister as a baby.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was a very popular way of-- everybody, I think, has a picture like that in Germany, when they were babies.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this is my father and mother, and my sister and myself, when I was a little baby.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
